name: Verify the Agency Number field is present under filter Edits Screen for policy reports

testSteps.description: 1: Verify the Agency Number field is present under filter Edits Screen for policy reports ({Reports=Inforce Policies})

children.description: Given underwriter is on home page of PAS
And select Reports 'Inforce Policies' from Policy
When user navigates to the filter edits screen
Then the field 'Agency Number' column should not be displayed for the mentioned reports
And the field Agency Number should be displayed in Filter Edits

testSteps.description: 2: Verify the Agency Number field is present under filter Edits Screen for policy reports ({Reports=Cancelled Policies})

children.description: Given underwriter is on home page of PAS

When user navigates to the filter edits screen
Then the field 'Agency Number' column should not be displayed for the mentioned reports
And the field Agency Number should be displayed in Filter Edits

dataTable.scenarioOutline:
Given underwriter is on home page of PAS
And user Navigates to Reports
And select Policy 'Policy' from Reports
And select Reports '<Reports>' from Policy
When user navigates to the filter edits screen
Then the field 'Agency Number' column should not be displayed for the mentioned reports
And the field Agency Number should be displayed in Filter Edits
